dct_description_sm: Taken from unknown atlas, dated 1908 in upper margin.
2 untitled ancillary maps of areas around Antananarivo and Fianarantsoa, showing boundaries with surrounding districts.
Shows railways, steamer routes, cities and regions, countries distinguished by coloring.
